---
title: Barbecue Chicken with Rainbow Pasta Salad
description: Almost all the colors of the rainbow make an appearance in this pasta salad standout. We’re talking red peppers, orange carrots, green scallions, and even purple cabbage. It’s light yet balanced and perfect for outdoor entertaining.
